3. Insertion Sort
Definition

Insert each element into its correct position.

Java Code
public class InsertionSort {
    public static void main(String[] args) {

        int arr[] = {5, 3, 8, 4, 2};

        for (int i = 1; i < arr.length; i++) {

            int key = arr[i];
            int j = i - 1;

            while (j >= 0 && arr[j] > key) {
                arr[j + 1] = arr[j];
                j--;
            }

            arr[j + 1] = key;
        }

        for (int num : arr)
            System.out.print(num + " ");
    }
}

Output

2 3 4 5 8

Time Complexity

Best: O(n)
Average: O(n²)
Worst: O(n²)

Space Complexity

O(1)